a0436abad98794a5ee6a","tid":717350,"uid":135827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T13:24:16.000Z","msg":"我夢入面個同學有補欣師，佢比學生嘅作文題目完全係出版社/坊間參考書嘅題目，想知咁樣做唔做得入佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"569e26c5ad30bb01a21c124f947ece01c1bc2ebb","tid":717350,"uid":147387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T17:03:46.000Z","msg":"迷乜鬼思？<br />\n咪抄kris lau神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"302671fff86f30525d144137d593483be52757de","tid":717350,"uid":6282,"like":1,"dislike":13,"score":-12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T17:45:09.000Z","msg":"打手們 算把啦<br />\n用最簡單邏輯已經KO你哋<br />\n首先，思齊有樣嘢叫名校試題庫<br />\n好多學校都係share啟思試題庫<br />\n而啲試卷係佢啲喺學校教既朋友比佢既<br />\n印喺筆記有幾出奇？<br />\n呢啲唔係抄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我自己都試過喺學校考試撞過同一樣既試卷 （棗香醉人嗰篇）<br />\n<br />\n一間小型補習社竟然吸引到燈塔派出打手攻擊<br />\n你哋可想而知思齊有幾勁 居心叵測<br />\n以前上堂都唔信佢話間補習社比大型補習社搞<br />\n依家信啦<br />\n<br />\n嗰種貼地係巨人學唔到㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢比我哋嗰種the sense of belongings <br />\n係你舉辦幾多場演唱會<br />\n派幾多本天書<br />\n有幾多篇離地範文<br />\n都比唔到 啲學生都學唔到嘢<br />\n<br />\n唔講咁多 廢事入錢你袋 <br />\n<br />\n任何人搞思齊 我會繼續用邏輯駁到你哋班打手無聲出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n都係發夢夢見"},{"pid":"26ab3489eb33476fb592d50f740d0a1b27366450","tid":717350,"uid":6282,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"ac8a9c1c0f68c39671b21557f74b8e1b5713bf32","tid":717350,"uid":192132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T03:13:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/26/110814_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F26%2F110814_d0b3244693